skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill is the voice-activated module of Free Press Publishing, based in Cheney, Wash. It will provide news headlines daily from the greater Cheney area. To access the news from your Alexa device, you'll need to enable the skill in your Alexa app. Once enabled, it will be added to your Flash Briefing. You can access it by saying, "Alexa, what's my flash briefing," or "Alexa, what's in the news."
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
